Benefits of Solar Energy
=========================

### Environmental Benefits
Solar energy is a clean and renewable source of energy, producing no greenhouse gas emissions or pollution.

### Economic Benefits
Installing a solar energy system can save homeowners $25,000 to over $110,000 over its lifetime.

### Health Benefits
Solar energy results in fewer people suffering from chronic bronchitis and other cardiovascular and respiratory diseases.

### Energy Independence
Solar energy allows homeowners to reduce their reliance on fossil fuels and grid-supplied power.